Validation gives this error message on a GeneralGlyph for rules which must reference them by MetaId:

0:Index objects should reference a valid SIdRef but Index [referencedAttribute=layout:metaidRef, arrayDimension=0] of object generalGlyph [id=Glyph__rule0, reference=null] references an unknown SBase.

To address this, the validation should likely allow the referencedAttribute to be an IdRef (i.e., a metaId).

Chris


